    %h1.py-3.title
      Pivotal Mentors "Learn To Code"
    %p.mt-1
      Starting in August of 2016 we partnered with
      = link_to('Pivotal Labs', 'https://pivotal.io/labs', target: '_blank')
      to an ongoing "Learn To Code" program we dubbed the "Pivotal Mentors Program".
      As the program has evolved we have integrated in more hands-on engineering
      and creative art activities in an attempt to explore a wider range of
      design oriented experiences.

